    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing At Stake is an open world action-adventure with a roguelike structure styled in the vein of classic n64 games, specifically taking inspiration from the first 3d Legend of Zelda games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252750/extras/eb5d5ba99c6e893f8027f352c027f801.avif?t=1770442165\" width=710 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within is an oblique dark fantasy world packed full of dungeons, ruins of a recently dead civilization, and colorful characters doing their best to survive in a seemingly hopeless world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help them make something of the scattered chaos that remains or set down your own path accumulating power as you scope out a land you'd been long isolated from. Whatever your path, tread carefully, as <strong>there is no coming back from death.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OVER A DECADE AGO, THE DOMINANT CIVILIZATION FELL.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252750/extras/d528a9a736a15e32044201bfad397979.avif?t=1770442165\" width=354 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STRUCK BY AN OTHERWORLDLY FORCE, MANIFESTED IN THE FORM OF A 100 QUADRILLION TON CONGLOMERATION OF ROCK, METAL, AND OTHER INDETERMINATE SUBSTANCES.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252750/extras/70857fef7e6b426d6f846b95f377503d.avif?t=1770442165\" width=354 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A WORLD IN TATTERS, STREWN BY PILES OF RUIN AND UNDYING, UNMANAGED MACHINERY REMAINS.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252750/extras/7a806bae3b826ace19abc390d5ed8882.avif?t=1770442165\" width=354 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > FORMERLY SUBJUGATED PEOPLES SPREAD OUTWARD FROM THEIR FORMERLY PENNED-IN CORNERS, TRYING TO MAKE SENSE OF THE RUBBLE AND THEIR IMPENDING DOOM.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252750/extras/ba9e61fe0381cb63519a0bc5ce1bce2c.avif?t=1770442165\" width=354 height=264 /></span></p>",
